<script>
   import Section from "./PageHome_Section.vue";
   export default {
      components: { Section },
      props: {
         isParentThin: { type: Boolean, default: false },
      },
   };
</script>

<template>
   <Section class="HomeSectionLocation" :isParentThin="isParentThin" title="Find Us">
      <iframe
         class="HomeSectionLocation-map"
         id="gmap_canvas"
         src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Freshnet%20Enterprise&t=&z=15&ie=UTF8&iwloc=&output=embed"
         frameborder="0"
         scrolling="no"
         marginheight="0"
         marginwidth="0"
      />
   </Section>
</template>

<style lang="scss" scoped>
   .HomeSectionLocation {
      grid-area: findUs;
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;

      --map-width: 100%;
      --map-height: 100%;
      --map-max-width: 100%;
      --map-max-height: 100%;

      .HomeSectionLocation-map {
         z-index: 1;
         text-align: right;
         width: var(--map-width);
         height: var(--map-height);
         max-width: var(--map-max-width);
         max-height: var(--map-max-height);
         background: white;
         aspect-ratio: 14/10;
         border: 0.1em solid hsla(0, 0%, 0%, 0.1);
      }
   }
</style>
